high_descs: Go straight then turn right, then turn left to face the stove.
Take the bowl from the cabinet beneath the counter, to the right of the stove.
Turn left, then turn left and go straight to the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Place the bowl in the left sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl in the sink.

high_descs: Walk towards the counter to the right of the stove.
Open the cabinet below the counter and take out the bowl.
Turn left, take a step forward, and then turn left towards the fridge.
Place the bowl in the fridge for it to cool and take it back out.
Turn right towards the sinks.
Place the bowl in the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled bowl in the left sink.

high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the small section of counter to the right of the oven.
Open the cabinet door that is to the right of the oven and remove the glass bowl, then close the door.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the fridge.

Open the fridge doors and place the bowl inside on the shelf in between the two tomatoes, then close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the now chilled bowl, then close the doors.
Turn right and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Place the chilled glass bowl in the leftmost sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl in the leftmost sink basin.

high_descs: Go to the counter that is next to the stove on the right.
Open the cabinet door.  Grab the bowl that is in the cabinet.
With the bowl go to the fridge.
Open the fridge.  Place the bowl on the second shelf.  Close the fridge.  Open the fridge and grab the bowl that is on the second shelf.
With the bowl turn and go to the sink.
Place the bowl in the sink that is on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Take a bowl to the fridge.
